name: Air Canada 777-333ER [C-FNNQ] Close Up Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
First time catching one of Air Canada's "sardine can" 77Ws, one of 5 such configured aircraft in the fleet at the moment. Here is fin number 745 landing at Vancouver International Airport on Runway 08L, with some sweet GE90 sound and spray! I really like how this clip turned out, the look of the aircraft on short final and the touchdown shot are just great. I hope you enjoy the video.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
